title: Santa Cruz In the Park: Kernside
description:
The Santa Cruz Skateboards team visited Sid Melvin's skate shop, The Bakersfield Skate Company, and then stopped by for a little session at the Kerside Skatepark DIY. In the Park by Strange Notes, featuring Sid Melvin, Emmanual Guzman, Justin Strubing, Ron Whaley, and Eric Dressen.

Music:
Restavrant "Yes, I guess"
